snippet.textDisplay: I lost my Grandfather to poor health back in 2018. He heard this song when it initially came out. I still remember listening to this song on the same day he passed. I still remember he would Video call me with my granny listening to this song, and tell me how much he loved me and missed me, living in Dubai. I thank Sachin and Jigar for making this song so close to me, so that i can remember my granddad with it.
